  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To test the efficacy of motorized cryotherapy on early effusion, and pain after ACL
      reconstruction
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      To test the efficacy of motorized cryotherapy on early effusion, and pain after ACL
      reconstruction compared to classical ice bagging
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
